Description:
  Generates a venue.yml file for a specific event in an event series.
  This will attempt to geocode the provided address and include the coordinates  and full address info in the generated file.
  We use nominatim (openstreetmap) by default, but including a Google Maps API key in .env may improve your results.

Example:
  bin/rails g venue --event=tiny-ruby-conf-2026 --name="Korjaamo Kino cinema" --address "Töölönkatu 51 A-B, 00250 Helsinki"

  This will create a venue file with geocoded coordinates and all address values.
    data/tiny-ruby-conf/tiny-ruby-conf-2026/venue.yml
